{"word":"ἀάατος","slug":"ἀάατος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n6\" key=\"a)a/atos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀάατος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἀάω</etym>) in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> </bibl> <pron extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pron\">̆̄̄̆</pron>, <sense id=\"n6.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">not to be injured, inviolable,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">νῦν μοι ὄμθσσον ἀ. Στυγὸς ὕδωρ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:14:271\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.271</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n6.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> </bibl> <pron extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pron\">̆̄̆̆</pron>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἄεθλος ἀ. ἐκτετέλεσται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:22:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.5</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:21:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.9</biblScope></bibl>, prob. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">unimpeachable,</tr_> i.e. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">decisive.</tr_> </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n6.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> later, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">invincible,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κάρτος ἀάᾰτος</